## **Franco Chains: The Strongest Chain Structure**

**The Franco chain is the most structurally durable chain type in Blue Nile's catalog — four links interlocking in a V-pattern with square cross-section, virtually kink-resistant and highly scratch-resistant.**

The Franco's square cross-section makes it the sturdiest chain for daily wear. Unlike rope chains (which can kink) or Figaro chains (where individual links can bend under stress), Franco chains maintain their structure under significant mechanical load.

For men with active lifestyles who want a gold chain that can withstand regular contact, the Franco is the recommended construction.

### **Diamond-Cut Square Franco — 4mm:**

**[22" Men's Diamond Cut Square Franco Chain in 14K Yellow Gold (4mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/22-mens-diamond-cut-square-franco-chain-in-14k-yellow-gold-4-mm-item-195653?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$2,818** (was $3,315, −15%, 12 reviews)

The most-reviewed chain in the entire Blue Nile men's catalog with 12 reviews. The 15% discount saves $497. At 4mm diamond-cut square Franco, this is the optimal balance of visual presence, daily-wear durability, and price.

The diamond-cut faceting on the square links catches light aggressively. **For active daily-wear buyers, this is the single best value recommendation in the catalog.**

