## **Specialty Chains: Anchor, Box, Wheat, Twisted Oval**

### **Anchor Chain (High Polish)**

The anchor (mariner) pattern features oval links with a central bar — modeled on ship anchor chains. The high-polish finish creates a clean, architectural look.

**[24" High Polish Anchor Chain in 14K Yellow Gold (3.8mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/24-high-polish-anchor-chain-in-14k-yellow-gold-38-mm-item-192922?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$2,210** (3 reviews)

At $2,210, the 3.8mm anchor chain is one of the best-value gold chains in the catalog — three reviews, 24" length, and a clean nautical aesthetic that works across casual and business casual settings.

### **Round Box Chain**

The box chain features square cross-section links creating a boxy, geometric pattern. It is popular as a pendant chain because its regular spacing holds pendants securely without tangling.

![22" Semi-Solid Men's Round Box Chain in 14k Yellow Gold (3.6 mm)](/images/2222-Semi-Solid-Mens-Round-Box-Chain-in-14k-Yellow-Gold-3.6-mm.png "2222 Semi Solid Mens Round Box Chain In 14k Yellow Gold 3.6 Mm")

**[22" Semi-Solid Men's Round Box Chain in 14K Yellow Gold (3.6mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/22-semi-solid-mens-round-box-chain-in-14k-yellow-gold-36-mm-item-201626?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$4,080** (available in multiple lengths)

### **Wheat Chain (White Gold)**

The wheat (spiga) chain features oval links angled at 45 degrees — creating a herringbone-like braided appearance with exceptional drape and comfort.

**[20" Wheat Chain Necklace in 14K White Gold (4.3mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/20-wheat-chain-necklace-in-14k-white-gold-43-mm-item-150503?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$2,116** (was $2,490, −15%)

The 15% discount on the wheat chain makes this the best-discounted specialty chain in the catalog. White gold construction at 4.3mm provides a refined, modern appearance.

### **Cable Chain (Open Link)**

The cable chain features simple round open links — the most basic chain construction and the most versatile pendant chain.

**[18" Round Open Link Cable Chain in 14K Yellow Gold (3.2mm)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/18-round-open-link-cable-chain-in-14k-yellow-gold-32-mm-item-150485?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$2,850** (available in multiple lengths)

### **Twisted Oval Link**

A distinctive specialty chain with twisted oval links creating a dynamic, three-dimensional appearance.

![20" Twisted Oval Link Chain Necklace in 14K Yellow Gold](/images/2022-Twisted-Oval-Link-Chain-Necklace-in-14K-Yellow-Gold.png "2022 Twisted Oval Link Chain Necklace In 14K Yellow Gold")

**[20" Twisted Oval Link Chain Necklace in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/necklaces/20-twisted-oval-link-chain-necklace-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-281695?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)** — **$10,965** (was $12,900, −15%)

The 15% discount saves $1,935. The twisted oval link is one of the most distinctive designs in the catalog — unlike standard cable or curb patterns, the twist creates continuous movement and visual interest.

